{"tid":1534624,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"如果發夢有人派ak47，你哋會唔會割","createTime":"2019-09-03T05:18:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-21T15:07:30.000Z","uid":38121,"like":110,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":73,"replies":[{"pid":"4f8b84c8d55bf705e82ddabcf9f89e268915d8a2","tid":1534624,"uid":38121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:18:16.000Z","msg":"忽發奇想咁多人話要革命，咁你哋又有冇勇氣好似美國人立國嘅拎起槍去革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4d6367177419a76c339b30383025169f98f58ff","tid":1534624,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:18:41.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f553cccd71d70e994a1cb4a85dd7958924c6aa85","tid":1534624,"uid":289649,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:20:37.000Z","msg":"明白大家呢排嘅士氣經過<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">831恐襲</span></span>同<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">901大撤退</span></span>之後好低落<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我同大家一樣都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但越係呢啲時候<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我地就越要堅持下去，<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">團結一致</span></span><br />\n唔好比林鄭見我地冇士氣而去捉多啲人<br />\n<br />\n以下兩篇文章<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">無論<span style=\"color: gold;\">和理非</span>，定係<span style=\"color: red;\">勇武</span>，都應該入黎，打返枝<span style=\"color: violet;\">強心針</span></span><br />\n<br />\n希望可以幫到大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記得share比身邊因近日事件而唔開心嘅朋友仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［全部人同我入黎］《致眾表》望各位香港市民出自己的一份綿力<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1532967\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1532967</a><br />\n<br />\n灰心喪志，是因為你看不見抗爭的前路<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1533741\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1533741</a>"},{"pid":"820b10b09e3260b47ed52530c6de9f202dd573ec","tid":1534624,"uid":16061,"like":48,"dislike":1,"score":47,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:23:33.000Z","msg":"傻傻地 你有槍派 大把未出過去嘅都即刻出"},{"pid":"a5b1a3bade1e083208b5f0ef89341365b01f0c69","tid":1534624,"uid":108814,"like":50,"dislike":0,"score":50,"quote":{"pid":"820b10b09e3260b47ed52530c6de9f202dd573ec","tid":1534624,"uid":16061,"like":48,"dislike":1,"score":47,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:23:33.000Z","msg":"傻傻地 你有槍派 大把未出過去嘅都即刻出"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:26:15.000Z","msg":"我諗呢一刻好多人唔驚死<br />\n係驚死得冇價值"},{"pid":"aa2fa068130fc55d649aa4ce54bd3ad6778f0799","tid":1534624,"uid":34293,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:02:52.000Z","msg":"一把AK可以燎原"},{"pid":"ad66d9af1e6145ac7457ac6ac459bba6b0f9f39a","tid":1534624,"uid":212336,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:04:18.000Z","msg":"咪撚問戇鳩問題,有槍有彈大把人仆街咁仆去上裝"},{"pid":"d16dc7904405389c8742383cd7b84dd767faf4bb","tid":15